data.description: Great sweat equity/rehab opportunity in Bolingbrook. This solid brick raised ranch home sits on a large corner lot. 2 Car detached garage and a generous sized back yard area. The main level features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, galley style kitchen and living room area. The lower level has a walkout to the back yard and has an additional bedroom, huge rec room and laundry room. over 1600 sq ft of living space.
